    "name": "C2M API v2 - Getting Started (With Examples)",
    "description": "Educational collection showing common API usage patterns with realistic test data.\n\n**Categories:**\n- **Most Frequently Used**: Essential calls every user needs\n- **Bulk Operations**: High-volume and batch processing\n- **Advanced Patterns**: Less common features and variations\n\n**How to use:**\n1. Set your `{{baseUrl}}` environment variable\n2. Review the realistic example data in each request\n3. Test the request as-is or modify values to match your needs\n4. Copy the pattern and adapt it to your use case\n\n**Note**: This collection contains realistic example values instead of placeholders. All data is fictitious and safe for testing.",
